Buyer & Buyer Agent to verify all measurements. Welcome to this charming 3-bedroom home nestled in St. Paul, boasting a spacious 2-car garage and a large driveway. As you step inside, the main floor living room graciously welcomes you into the updated eat-in kitchen, complete with sleek stainless steel appliances and a convenient gas range.
The main level also hosts 3 bedrooms and a well-appointed bathroom, ensuring comfort and convenience. Downstairs, ample storage awaits in the basement, offering the opportunity to create additional living space to suit your needs.
Conveniently, the garage provides easy access from the house, while the large backyard offers privacy and security with its full fencing.
Enjoy the convenience of quick access to Interstate 94, and relish in the proximity to a variety of dining options, including restaurants, fast food establishments, and a shopping center, all within walking distance.
